## ðŸ’¡ Project Introduction

**"Can we solve complex money transfer procedures with just one line of chat?"**

Traditional mobile banking apps required users to navigate through numerous depths and input processes to transfer money. OnelineBank is a fintech solution that addresses this inconvenience by introducing a **Conversational UI**.

When users express their transfer intent in everyday language, the app analyzes it and automatically executes the transfer process. By **integrating 'chatting', the most familiar experience, into financial services**, we maximized usability.

