#### 3. Conversational Money Transfer (NLP-based Parsing)
<ImageDescription src="/images/bank/bank03.webp" alt="Chatting page">
  **This is the core feature.** The app analyzes natural language text entered by users (e.g., "Send 50,000 won to mom") and automatically extracts recipient, bank, and amount information.
  <br/>
  1. <strong>Text Parsing:</strong> Recognizes account information and amounts from unstructured text using regular expressions
  2. <strong>User Confirmation:</strong> Implements bot interaction that asks users to confirm if the recognized information is correct
  3. <strong>Security Authentication:</strong> Enforces biometric authentication (Face ID/Touch ID) before final transfer
  4. <strong>API Call:</strong> Requests actual transfer transactions through Woori Bank Open API
</ImageDescription>

